1 Corona uses integrated Lua layered on top of C++/OpenGL to build graphic
 applications. The software has two operational modes: the Corona Simulator and Corona Native. With the Corona Simulator, you build your app directly from the Corona Simulator. Corona Native allows you use Xcode or Android Studio to build your app and include native features
